        individual differences in susceptibility to <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">Alzheimer disease</ENAMEX> is genetic, although the
        genes involved have not yet been completely discovered [<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">15</TIMEX>]. The balance of the explanation
        lies in environmental influences and behavioral health practices, alone or in interaction
