        For older <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">adults</ENAMEX>, health practices that could influence the brain include sound
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">nutrition</ENAMEX>, sufficient sleep, stress management, treatment of mood or <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">anxiety disorders</ENAMEX>,
